HEADWORD: Gonozooid
<hw>Gon`o*zo"oid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/
offspring + E. <ets>zooid</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A sexual
zooid, or medusoid bud of a hydroid; a gonophore. See
